[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    614[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     The lab feed reports positive count and total tests. We convert
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    615[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     to a positivity rate and then to an estimated weekly incidence
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    616[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     using the population denominator. Production maintains a
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    617[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     proper test-positivity-to-incidence model that accounts for
