[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    857[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                 effective_weight = feed_spec["fusion_weight"] * correction
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    858[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                 weights.append(effective_weight)
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    859[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    860[0m:[38;5;10m[49m             if not estimates:
