[49m[38;5;10m+     940[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ## Step 3: Per-Model Forecast Generation
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     941[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     942[0m:[38;5;10m[49m Each model family runs in parallel on the nowcast-conditioned input. The demo runs a Bayesian SEIR compartmental model and a statistical ARIMA baseline. The compartmental model uses the nowcast as the initial condition and projects forward under sampled SEIR parameter posteriors. The ARIMA model uses the harmonized panel directly with a basic AR(2) MA(1) recursion.
