[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     953[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     954[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     where beta = R0 * gamma / (1 - immunity_share). The demo
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     955[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     discretizes to weekly steps with simple Euler integration.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     956[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Production uses RK4 or scipy's odeint, and replaces the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     957[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     closed-form Monte Carlo sampling here with PyMC/Stan NUTS
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     958[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     on the joint parameter posterior.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     959[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     960[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
