[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1083[0m:[38;5;10m[49m class StatisticalARIMABaseline:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1084[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """Simplified ARIMA(p,d,q)-style statistical baseline.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1085[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1086[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     The demo implements an AR(2) MA(1) recursion with manually-set
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1087[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     coefficients fit via simple OLS on the harmonized panel's
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1088[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     primary signal. Production uses statsmodels SARIMAX with proper
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1089[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     auto-order selection, seasonality terms, and exogenous covariates.
