[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1841[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> latest panel row: {'epi_week': '2026-w21', 'lab_pcr_positivity': 65.4, ...}
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1842[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
