[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1844[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> nowcast for last week: p10=68.2, p50=82.1, p90=98.8
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1845[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> nowcast horizon: 4 weeks back
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1846[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1847[0m:[38;5;10m[49m [step 3] run_per_model_forecasts
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1848[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> seir-age-stratified-v3 (compartmental): horizon-1 p50=88.4
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1849[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> arima-baseline-v2 (statistical): horizon-1 p50=78.1
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1850[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1851[0m:[38;5;10m[49m [step 4] run_ensemble
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1852[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> ensemble method: wis_weighted
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1853[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> per-model weights: {'seir-age-stratified-v3': 0.54, 'arima-baseline-v2': 0.46}
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1854[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> horizon-1 p50: 83.6, p10: 65.4, p90: 102.7
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1855[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1856[0m:[38;5;10m[49m [step 5a] compute_holdout_calibration
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1857[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> seir-age-stratified-v3: coverage_50=0.50, coverage_80=0.75, coverage_95=0.93, WIS=21.4
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1858[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> arima-baseline-v2: coverage_50=0.25, coverage_80=0.50, coverage_95=0.75, WIS=29.6
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1859[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> drift alarms: 1
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1860[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1861[0m:[38;5;10m[49m [step 5b] compose_scenario_forecasts
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1862[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> scenario baseline_no_intervention: peak_p50=124.8 at 2026-w27, p10/p90 range=[82.1, 178.3]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1863[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> scenario moderate_npi_indoor_masking: peak_p50=96.4 at 2026-w29, p10/p90 range=[60.2, 142.8]
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1864[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1865[0m:[38;5;10m[49m [step 5c] deliver_forecast
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1866[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> wrote 8 horizons to DynamoDB
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1867[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> wrote 2 scenarios to registry
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1868[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> emitted 1 EventBridge events
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1869[0m:[38;5;10m[49m   -> raised 1 CloudWatch alarms
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1870[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    1871[0m:[38;5;10m[49m === Sample DynamoDB record (horizon-1) ===
